OL,3,C'Monster' used fake accounts to
OL,4,Cencourage teenage girl to self harm
OL,6,FA father-of-two has become the first
OL,7,Fperson in the UK to be convicted of
OL,8,Fencouraging a schoolgirl to self harm
OL,9,F- after using a number of fake social
OL,10,Fmedia accounts to bombard her.
OL,12,FKarl Davies, 42, used multiple online
OL,13,Faccounts to speak to the then 13-year-
OL,14,Fold girl from Stockport, before
OL,15,Ftravelling to see her and engage in
OL,16,Fsexual acts.
