OL,6,FOn one occasion Davies, who was
OL,7,Fmarried with two boys both under the
OL,8,Fage of 10, encouraged the schoolgirl
OL,9,Fto harm herself, asking for pictures
OL,10,Fof her carrying out the acts.
OL,12,FHe was finally arrested after his
OL,13,Fvictim told her stepmother of the
OL,14,Fabuse, and a video of Davies sexually
OL,15,Fabusing the girl was found on her
OL,16,Fphone by police.
