OL,6,FThe quantity surveyor from the Wirral,
OL,7,Fwho showed "no pity and no mercy" for
OL,8,Fthe "catastrophic" impact on his
OL,9,Fvictim, was convicted of 17 offences
OL,10,Frelating to the schoolgirl aged
OL,11,Fbetween 13 and 14.
OL,13,FHe is only the second person to be
OL,14,Fconvicted of the crime since it was
OL,15,Fintroduced in January 2024 - and the
OL,16,Ffirst to be convicted for targeting
OL,17,Fsomeone under the age of 18 - under
OL,18,FSection 184 of the Online Safety Act
OL,19,F2023.
