OL,6,FJailing him for 20 years at Manchester
OL,7,FCrown Court Judge Hilary Manley
OL,8,Fimposed an extended sentence on Davies
OL,9,Fto reflect his "depraved and sadistic"
OL,10,Fcrimes.
OL,12,FJudge Manley said: "To encourage a
OL,13,Fvulnerable young girl to inflict harm
OL,14,Fon herself for your sexual
OL,15,Fgratification really does plumb the
OL,16,Fdepths of abhorrent behaviour."
