OL,3,C'Monster' used fake accounts to
OL,4,Cencourage teenage girl to self harm
OL,6,FThe court heard Davies first made
OL,7,Fcontact pretending to be a 14-year-old
OL,8,Fboy on social media chatroom site
OL,9,FDiscord, before moving their
OL,10,Fconversations to Snapchat.
OL,12,FHe went on to contact her from six
OL,13,Fdifferent accounts each with their own
OL,14,Fpersonas, but all claiming to be adult
OL,15,Fmen from the Merseyside area.
OL,17,FSome of the usernames used include
OL,18,Fbshekehrbrkgo, scousechris, Lee33Liv.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/16
