OL,3,C'Monster' used fake accounts to
OL,4,Cencourage teenage girl to self harm
OL,6,FMany of the accounts threatened the
OL,7,Fvictim with claims they would hurt
OL,8,Fher, while one of his accounts, where
OL,9,Fhe posed as someone called 'Mark',
OL,10,Fpromised to protect her from the other
OL,11,Fmen.
OL,13,FDetective Sergeant Rob Griffiths led
OL,14,Fthe investigation for Greater
OL,15,FManchester Police, and said he had
OL,16,Fnever seen such a sophisticated effort
OL,17,Fto target a young person.
