OL,6,FPosing as Mark, Davies picked her up
OL,7,Ffrom school in "broad daylight" to
OL,8,Fsexually abuse her in his car on four
OL,9,Foccasions in the summer of 2024.
OL,11,FOn one occasion he even brought her
OL,12,Ftools to harm herself before
OL,13,Fencouraging her to use them and send
OL,14,Fhim pictures and videos of her doing
OL,15,Fit.
OL,17,FWhen the victim told another online
OL,18,Fpersona, who turned out to be Davies,
OL,19,Fabout meeting up with "Mark", he said:
OL,20,F"This is dodgy, don't go through with
OL,21,Fit."
