OL,6,FThe court was told that at home,
OL,7,FDavies' wife suspected her husband was
OL,8,Fhaving an affair and found the
OL,9,Fvictim's number on his phone.
OL,11,FShe called the victim, who picked up
OL,12,Fthe call, but quickly hung up. Davies'
OL,13,Fwife said she did not realise the girl
OL,14,Fwas underage from the short phone call.
OL,16,FPolice first began investigating
OL,17,FDavies in July 2024 after the victim
OL,18,Ftold a friend she was going to meet
OL,19,Fhim. The friend told school staff, who
OL,20,Fthen reported it to the police.
