OL,6,FThe victim initially did not want to
OL,7,Fspeak to the police, and claimed
OL,8,Fnothing had happened with Davies, but
OL,9,Fafter working with a social worker
OL,10,Fdecided to give a three hour police
OL,11,Finterview in January 2025.
OL,13,FAfter her interview, in which she
OL,14,Fexplained the abusive and threatening
OL,15,Fmessages she received from the various
OL,16,Faccounts, detectives believed they
OL,17,Fwere looking for six male suspects
OL,18,Frather than one person.
