OL,6,FEventually, police were able to track
OL,7,Fdown Davies after the victim described
OL,8,Fthe make and model of the car he
OL,9,Fdrove; a SEAT Ateca.
OL,11,FPolice were able to track all of the
OL,12,FSEAT Ateca's over a two day period and
OL,13,Fidentified his car by a distinctive
OL,14,Fair freshener she had described.
OL,16,FThrough ANPR cameras, officers were
OL,17,Fable to track Davies' route from his
OL,18,Ffront door, and identify the owner.
