OL,6,FPolice analysts were then able to link
OL,7,Fhim to the account of a supposed 14-
OL,8,Fyear-old boy on Discord.
OL,10,FIt was only when officers raided
OL,11,FDavies' home that they discovered all
OL,12,Fsix accounts were sending messages
OL,13,Ffrom the same location.
OL,15,FOn 11 February 2025, Davies was
OL,16,Farrested in his home. He showed no
OL,17,Femotion but pleaded with his wife to
OL,18,Fstay calm, before providing a no
OL,19,Fcomment interview.
