OL,7,Fwas so concerned she actually provided
OL,8,Fa statement which actually greatly
OL,9,Fassisted with getting Karl sent to
OL,10,Fprison."
OL,12,FDespite admitting to the charges,
OL,13,FDavies told probation services that he
OL,14,Fwas not sexually interested in
OL,15,Fchildren, even though he abused the
OL,16,Fgirl in her school uniform and told
OL,17,Fher she had a "good body for a 14-year-
OL,18,Fold", the court heard.
