OL,6,FStacey Gosling, Senior Crown
OL,7,FProsecutor for CPS North West, said:
OL,8,F"As a seasoned prosecutor of grooming
OL,9,Fcases I have never before seen such
OL,10,Fsophisticated methods used to target a
OL,11,Fyoung person.
OL,13,F"Karl Davies went to great lengths to
OL,14,Fhide his identity and position himself
OL,15,Fas the child's protector when he was
OL,16,Fanything but.
OL,18,F"I can only hope that as Davies begins
OL,19,Fhis prison sentence, the victim can
OL,20,Fbegin to move forward knowing her vile
OL,21,Fabuser has been brought to justice."
